---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lang = 'en';
const pageTitle = 'Privacy policy - Alexis Fiska';
const pageDescription =
  'This policy explains how your data is collected and used when you browse the site and use the contact form.';
---
<BaseLayout lang={lang} title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Privacy policy</h1>
  <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <p>
      This site does not collect personal data other than the information you choose to provide via
      the contact form. Data submitted through this form is routed through the Formspree service. It
      is used solely to respond to your request and is kept only as long as necessary for follow‑up.
      You may request its deletion at any time by writing to
      <a href="mailto:contact@alexis-fiska.dev">contact@alexis-fiska.dev</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      For audience measurement we use <strong>Plausible Analytics</strong>, a privacy‑friendly
      solution that sets no cookies and collects no personally identifiable information. Only
      anonymous statistics are recorded (page views, referrers, etc.).
    </p>
    <p>
      Under the GDPR you have the right to access, rectify and delete your data. To exercise these
      rights or ask a question about the privacy policy, please contact us by email.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>